People are sharing with CC licenses in
34 languages with more than 90 million views
of CC’s deeds in the last 10 years.

communities on every continent (yes, even Antarctica). A significant
milestone was the 2013 launch of Version 4.0 and CC’s first official
translation policy for internationalizing the license suite. To date, the 4.0
